al cases \r\nhttp://youtu.be/FeGaGj_ePlU\r\n\r\nDiscussing the unfairness of federal plea bargaining process. \r\nhttp://youtu.be/iqtD0AYNS9I\r\n\r\nNFL’s handling of Ray Rice assault case\r\nhttp://youtu.be/wtRuY41IaB8\r\n\r\nFIOS1 News\r\nNovember 24, 2014 Mr. Kousouros was interviewed as a legal expert while awaiting the Ferguson Grand Jury decision.\r\nhttp://youtu.be/xJiFxRUh3ek\r\n\r\n', 'Press/Media', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1080-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-21 16:50:00', '2015-04-21 20:50:00', '', 1080, 'http://localhost:8888/kousouros_law/1080-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
